recommended_tv.title: Recommended TV
recommended_tv.description: We picked these out just for you.

0300010104.title: LA's Finest
0300010104.description: A former DEA agent with a complicated past gets partnered with a working mom when she takes a new job as an LAPD detective in this Bad Boys spinoff.

0300006999.title: Bizarre Murders
0300006999.description: Told by former detectives through vivid re-enactments, hear stories of true crimes committed by the unlikely and that border on the outlandish.

0300009901.title: Lovecraft Country
0300009901.description: Atticus Freema joins his friend Letitia and his uncle George to embark on a road trip across 1950's Jim Crow America in search of his missing father.

0300004985.title: Midsomer Murders
0300004985.description: A married veteran Detective Chief Inspector and his young sergeant investigate murders in the quaint, quirky villages of England’s Midsomer County.

0300005344.title: The Shannara Chronicles (Español)
0300005344.description: Los demonios atrapados por milenios en un árbol que está muriendo amenazan con dominar un mundo donde la magia ha reemplazado la tecnología.

0300008637.title: Mike Tyson Mysteries
0300008637.description: The adult animation classic series featuring the voice talents of Mike Tyson and Norm MacDonald sees the champion boxer taking on weekly mysteries!

0300005940.title: Foster Sin
0300005940.description: This video series aims to raise awareness of the mistreatment of children in the foster care system and serve as a guide to improve young lives.

0300010320.title: Murder Comes to Town
0300010320.description: Friends and family recount personal stories of horrific crimes that took place in some of the most unassuming places throughout America's heartland.

0300010409.title: Taken
0300010409.description: While dealing with a personal tragedy that shakes his world, CIA agent Bryan Mills fights to overcome the incident and exact revenge.

02067.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!
02067.description: Follows the adventures of teenager Yugi, whose magical secret comes to life when he plays his favorite card game: 'Duel Monsters.'

0300000125.title: Welcome Back, Kotter
0300000125.description: This series follows teacher Gabe Kotter as he returns to his former high school to teach a remedial class of students known as the “Sweathogs.”

0300009994.title: Ma's House
0300009994.description: When Ma finds herself in trouble and on house arrest, her son, Jarad, allows her to live with his family.

0300005712.title: MasterChef Australia
0300005712.description: Hopeful home chefs show off their culinary skills in a vicious yet delicious battle for the ultimate title of Australian MasterChef.

0300007679.title: The Chosen
0300007679.description: Witness the life of Christ through the ordinary people who connected with him through miracles and everyday interactions that changed the world.

04430.title: Haven
04430.description: Crime series with supernatural shadings as an FBI agent assigned to a case in Maine finds herself on the trail of unexplained and spooky occurrences.

0300008198.title: Are We There Yet?
0300008198.description: A divorced mother marries a former athlete, creating a hilarious and often chaotic blended household, where squabbles are always overcome by love.

04294.title: Dance Moms
04294.description: Popular reality series following the tough love teaching by a dance instructor-choreographer of talented tweens and her occasional parental run-ins.

0300010224.title: Scarecrow and Mrs. King
0300010224.description: A single mother in suburban Washington, D.C. discovers she has a talent for espionage work when she meets a dashing undercover agent.

0300008167.title: Bad Girls Club
0300008167.description: A group of women with anger and control issues come together and try to improve themselves. But moving forward isn’t going to be easy.

0300009519.title: Spook Show 17
0300009519.description: An innovator makes his own reality TV show about how he and his wife led a crew to build the craziest, most elaborate haunted house in the galaxy.

04718.title: LEGO Ninjago Masters of Spinjitzu
04718.description: Peace has returned to Ninjago, but the four ninja warriors swear to protect and learn to master their Golden Weapons awaiting Lord Garmadon's return.

0300004999.title: Garfield and Friends
0300004999.description: Lazy, lasagna-loving cat Garfield has fun adventures with his pal Odie and owner Jon.

01627.title: Hunter X Hunter (English Subtitle)
01627.description: A young boy, who dreams of being a hunter like his father, must pass the notoriously difficult and dangerous Hunter Qualification Exam.

0300006778.title: Barney & Friends
0300006778.description: Gather your little ones around to hear from the friendliest purple dinosaur, who has a passion for learning with his favorite friends!

0300008052.title: What's Happening!!
0300008052.description: Classic ‘70s series about L.A. high school journalist Raj and his best friends Rerun and Dwayne whose antics are never unseen by his nosy sister Dee.

0300007078.title: Soap
0300007078.description: A satire on soap operas, this zany comedy threw together a group of family members whose lives were larger than life and never dull! Stories take some bizarre and unexpected turns as the daily living of the wealthy Tate family and the blue-collar Campbell family unfold.

02348.title: Duck Dynasty
02348.description: Follow the Robertsons as they run a multi-million dollar sporting empire and face everything from beavers to business deals, in this reality series.

0300000080.title: The Book of Negroes
0300000080.description: Kidnapped in Africa and enslaved in South Carolina as a girl, a woman attempts to secure her freedom in eighteenth century North America.

0300010082.title: Third Watch
0300010082.description: A drama about the brave and dedicated people who serve as paramedics, firefighters, and police on the “third watch,” the 3:00 PM to 11:00 PM shift.

0300008580.title: Real Husbands of Hollywood
0300008580.description: Kevin Hart and his friends parody their own lives, where the pressures of spousal stardom are almost too much to handle, in this faux-reality satire.

0300009966.title: The Twilight Zone
0300009966.description: In this revival of the classic anthology series, host Forest Whitaker leads us on a mysterious journey into the deepest recesses of the human psyche.

0300008457.title: The Jeffersons
0300008457.description: Class, race, neighbors, family, and all kinds of clashes make for classic comedy in this beloved series about a family’s move on up to luxury living.

0300008639.title: The Steve Harvey Show
0300008639.description: Steve Harvey's sitcom from the WB network is classic '90s comedy about a musician-turned-teacher who teaches his unruly students a thing or three!

0300010076.title: Eight Is Enough
0300010076.description: This touching series follows a close-knit family as they face the hardships and challenges of the ups and downs of everyday life in a family of ten.

0300000124.title: Gilligan's Island
0300000124.description: Shipwrecked on an uncharted South Pacific island, seven castaways struggle to survive the outdoors—and each other—in this wacky classic comedy series.

02166.title: Merlin
02166.description: The young wizard Merlin must keep his talent hidden in a kingdom where magic is banned as he and the future King Arthur face their destinies.

0300009902.title: Southland
0300009902.description: When a seasoned cop is assigned to train a rookie, his no-nonsense approach makes the young man question if he has what it takes to become an officer.

0300006058.title: The Client List
0300006058.description: Jennifer Love Hewitt stars as Riley, a newly single mother who accepts employment at a day spa which offers some scandalous services.

0300009077.title: The Temptations
0300009077.description: One of Motown's most successful vocal acts was forced to battle prejudice, betrayal, drug abuse and more to become R&B and soul music royalty.

0300008640.title: Love, Diana by pocket.watch
0300008640.description: Join your imaginative hosts Diana and Roma as they go on magical adventures where learning is fun and anything is possible if you work together!

0300005636.title: The Fall
0300005636.description: The acclaimed crime series about a grim and gripping battle of wits between a brazen serial killer and a top-notch detective out to stop him.

0300010390.title: Extreme Cheapskates
0300010390.description: Spotlighting frugalists who will do anything to save a penny, this series explores the extreme lengths people will go to cut costs in their lives.

0300000087.title: Deputy
0300000087.description: When an elected sheriff dies, an arcane rule in the county charter, forged back in the Wild West, suddenly thrusts the most unlikely man into the job.

0300006035.title: Generation War
0300006035.description: Five young German friends are forced to navigate the everyday realities and the unconscionable moral compromises of life under Hitler's reign.

0300006855.title: Scooby-Doo and Scrappy-Doo
0300006855.description: Everyone’s favorite mystery-solving Great Dane is here to find clues, along with a little help from his energetic nephew and four human companions.

04893.title: McGraw Avenue
04893.description: In a notorious Detroit neighborhood, two men with different goals navigate the streets and deal with complex characters, to both survive and dominate.

02158.title: Q.I.
02158.description: QIis the Rose d'Or comedy quiz show full of quirky facts in which contestants are rewarded more if their answers are 'quite interesting'.

0300009246.title: Line of Duty
0300009246.description: Under the supervision of Superintendent Ted Hastings, British detectives in anti-corruption police unit AC-12 investigate suspected dirty cops.

0300009344.title: MasterChef
0300009344.description: Returning contestants vie for the top prize as MasterChef reopens its doors to some of the most memorable cooks in the competition’s history.

02383.title: Mutant X
02383.description: A genetic engineer goes on the run with his four created mutants while seeking their own kind while a shady government operative tracks them down.

0300010244.title: Miami Vice
0300010244.description: From executive producer Michael Mann comes the explosive, groundbreaking detective show that redefined the word "cool” in the mid-1980s.

0300010053.title: Fantasy Island (2021 Series)
0300010053.description: This modern drama series takes place at a luxury resort, where any fantasy requested by guests is fulfilled—although they rarely turn out as expected.

0300009219.title: Quantico
0300009219.description: FBI recruits form friendships while training at Quantico Base. But relationships are tested when one of them becomes a suspect in a terrorist attack.

0300007799.title: Blue Mountain State
0300007799.description: Three new athletes on a top college football team learn the extreme high and low of being among the chosen few who are worshiped and tested on campus.

0300000007.title: Farmer Wants a Wife
0300000007.description: This series follows four hard-working farmers in search of real, lasting love.

04638.title: Dark Shadows
04638.description: The classic, gothic, daytime TV series about a tormented vampire, freed from his grave after 200 years, who returns home to protect his loved ones.

0300000158.title: Hemlock Grove
0300000158.description: As a once-vibrant and now struggling community’s secrets begin to unravel, Hemlock Grove forces us to ask: What is the true nature of a monster?

0300000081.title: Hell on Wheels
0300000081.description: An epic story of post-Civil War America, focusing on a Confederate soldier who sets out to exact revenge on the Union soldiers who killed his wife.

0300009738.title: Sister, Sister
0300009738.description: Identical twins, separated at birth and adopted by different families, finally meet and try to bring their two very different parents together.

0300006868.title: Fantasy Island
0300006868.description: Dreams come true, for better or worse, in a tropical paradise, where a charming, enigmatic host and his diminutive assistant guide your magical visit.

0300008306.title: Next Level Chef
0300008306.description: Celebrity chef Gordon Ramsay hosts ambitious chefs facing unique cooking challenges, in a culinary competition to be the food world’s next superstar.

0300007162.title: Hotel Hell
0300007162.description: Gordon Ramsay travels the U.S.A. to give clueless hotel, B&B, and inn owners some grumpy hell of his own over dead bugs, gross sheets, dust, and more!

0300006728.title: Columbo
0300006728.description: This beloved series features the brilliant bumbling detective who despite his easygoing nature, always manages to crack the case.

0300006608.title: Bewitched
0300006608.description: The beloved TV series about a beautiful witch who marries an executive and starts a family as a housewife, much to the dismay of her powerful mother.

0300006856.title: The Flintstones
0300006856.description: Laugh along with the classic misadventures of two modern-day Stone Age families living amongst dinosaurs, doing their best in prehistoric times.

0300008432.title: The Oblongs
0300008432.description: An eccentric family lives downstream from a toxic waste site, and finds that life is always presenting a series of unusual challenges for them.

0300008079.title: The Bernie Mac Show
0300008079.description: Bernie Mac stars as a stand up comic who, alongside his businesswoman wife, must take in his sister's three kids while she's in rehab.

0300008430.title: How the West Was Won
0300008430.description: A Virginia-based family leaves their home to bravely travel across the country and make a new life in the wild, untamed American West.

0300010071.title: Babylon 5
0300010071.description: 2258 CE. The lone space station Babylon 5 stands as the last and best hope for peace between a hundred worlds, alien and human alike.

0300010267.title: Cake Boss
0300010267.description: Take a peek into the operations of Carlo's Bake Shop, where you'll find family, relationships, drama, and the most spectacular cakes ever made.

01077.title: Wildfire
01077.description: Fresh out of juvenile hall, Kris gets a chance at responsibility with a job on a struggling family ranch but soon gets caught up in complicated drama.

0300006821.title: Ambitions
0300006821.description: Two top Atlanta lawyers compete in personal and professional endeavors, in a battle of ambitions that so often gets out of control.

02914.title: Forensic Files
02914.description: Witnesses, investigators and medical experts lend their unique perspective on true crime in every episode of this long-running docuseries.

04753.title: Beowulf: Return to the Shieldlands
04753.description: In a world of danger populated by both humans and fantastical creatures, Beowulf must slowly reconnect with the notion of family and home.

03697.title: V
03697.description: When human-looking aliens known as Visitors appear in every major city U.S. promoting peace, an FBI counter-terrorist discovers their deadly plot.

0300004988.title: Fugget About It
0300004988.description: A former New York mobster joins the Witness Protection Program, which relocates him and his family, who must adjust to life in Saskatchewan, Canada.

0300007917.title: Secrets and Lies
0300007917.description: Juliette Lewis stars as a determined and brilliant detective whose latest murder case challenges her and her team with a family’s secrets and lies.

0300000159.title: Hannibal
0300000159.description: An FBI investigator with the ability to empathize with psychopaths is assigned to work with renowned psychiatrist—and secret cannibal—Hannibal Lecter.

0300010296.title: Mysteries at the Museum
0300010296.description: From ghost ships to wooden currency to a presidential cheese wheel, Don Wildman unearths unusual relics from the world's greatest institutions.

0300009178.title: The Dirty D
0300009178.description: Detroit's hottest nightclub is a world of drugs, sex, and money run by a shady power couple. Here there are no rules, and everyone plays for keeps.

02081.title: My Crazy Ex
02081.description: This docu-reality series tells the extraordinary but true stories of relationships that went awry when one partner’s behavior morphed from romantic to excessive to extreme.

03577.title: Bring It
03577.description: A tough but fierce dance coach trains an elite group of hip-hop majorettes, the Dancing Dolls, to compete across their local region.

0300006335.title: Detectorists
0300006335.description: Follow two oddball metal detectorists as they painstakingly plough through the literal and figurative tracks and fields of life in search of treasure.

03773.title: Unsealed Alien Files
03773.description: Investigate released documents regarding alien and UFO encounters, made accessible to the public in 2011 by the Freedom of Information Act. We investigate mass UFO sightings, personal abductions, government cover-ups and breaking alien news from around the world. We delve into the "photoshopping" of space, the value of Wikileaks, and the role social media plays in alien stories.

04717.title: Cosmos: A Spacetime Odyssey
04717.description: Join acclaimed astrophysicist Neil deGrasse Tyson on a journey through space and time in an effort to discover humanity’s place within the universe.

0300007796.title: Project Runway
0300007796.description: Models and fashion icons judge the works of clothing designers in this intense reality competition series that showcases up-and-coming artists.

0300010279.title: Gypsy Sisters
0300010279.description: This reality series takes viewers on a wild ride through the traditions, culture, and joy of the gypsy community in West Virginia.

017.title: Pound Puppies
017.description: A team of fearless dogs is on a mission to find homes for puppies in need. Once you're a pound puppy, you're always a pound puppy!

0300005157.title: Super Wings
0300005157.description: The action-packed preschool series features an adorable jet, who travels the world with his amazing plane pals, delivering packages to kids.

0300010238.title: Bad Girls All-Star Battle
0300010238.description: Bad Girls All-Star Battle features fun, over-the-top physical and mental challenges that will test the limits of the world's feistiest ladies.

03320.title: Hell's Kitchen
03320.description: Renowned restauranteur Gordon Ramsay hosts a fierce competition for aspiring chefs, as they vie for a prestigious job at one of his eateries.

0300010081.title: Nikita
0300010081.description: Betrayed by the secret government agency that made her an assassin, the charming and deadly Nikita makes it her mission to undermine the organization.

0300006854.title: Scooby-Doo Where Are You?
0300006854.description: The classic adventures of the lovable Great Dane and his human companions as they hunt for clues, hungry for a solution to mysteries and a snack.

0300009281.title: Everybody Hates Chris
0300009281.description: Comedian Chris Rock narrates the hilarious, touching story of a teenager growing up as the eldest of three children in Brooklyn during the 1980s.

0300010281.title: Breaking Amish
0300010281.description: Follow young adults from the Amish and Mennonite communities as they leave their homes to experiment with "new world" freedoms in New York City.

0300000119.title: The Facts of Life
0300000119.description: Four teens, each with their own backgrounds and personalities, become inseparable friends when they’re brought together at Eastland Academy for girls.

0300009446.title: Madre (Doblado)
0300009446.description: Una maestra sustituta, se da cuenta que su estudiante está siendo abusada. Decide tomar el asunto en sus manos, pero debe vivir con las consecuencias.

0300010397.title: How It's Made
0300010397.description: This series explores the fascinating world of how everyday items are manufactured and produced—anything from toothpicks, to pantyhose, to gummy candy.

0300010385.title: My Big Fat American Gypsy Wedding
0300010385.description: Watch as this series takes you through the superstitions, customs, and wedding celebrations of the gypsy communities throughout America.

0300006059.title: Kevin Can Wait
0300006059.description: A newly retired police officer has to reconsider his plans when his daughter announces she’s dropping out of college to support her fiancé.

0300006767.title: Heartland
0300006767.description: Alberta sisters and their grandfather spend their years on the family ranch, where they must work through complicated issues together.

04631.title: Degrassi: The Next Generation
04631.description: Long-running TV-series, acclaimed for its powerful realism in taking on the life-changing issues facing a group of friends at a Toronto high school.

03646.title: Little Women: Atlanta
03646.description: There's no shortage of excitement in this circle of friends as they face the daily challenges that come with being a little person in the big city.

0300007764.title: Pokémon the Series: Black & White
0300007764.description: Ash and Pikachu are off to the distant Unova region, where they'll encounter new friends, new rivals, new challenges, and all-new Pokémon! Upon arrival, Ash meets aspiring Dragon Master Iris, full of spirit and determination, and Pokémon Connoisseur Cilan, who is always available to lend his expertise. Above all, Ash will need plenty of new Pokémon on his team if he wants to win Unova's tournaments and Gym badges. Following his every move is the criminal trio of Team Rocket, with sinister new schemes and a fresh resolve to catch Pikachu! Then there's the mysterious N...is he a friend or a foe, and what is his connection with the secret organization known as Team Plasma? And what is Team Plasma planning to do with one of the Legendary Pokémon of the Unova region? Once this adventure starts, the excitement won't stop!

0300007193.title: Strawberry Shortcake's Berry Bitty Adventures
0300007193.description: This lovely spin-off of the beloved original series takes place in the fanciful community of Berry Bitty City, complete with new adventures.

0300005163.title: The Masked Singer
0300005163.description: Celebrity performers, costumed to conceal their identities but dropping hints along the way, compete each week as one is eliminated and unmasked.
